Common:
    Vundle is used as plugin manager

Installation: 

	git clone https://github.com/ejaskal/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim


Create symlinks:
	
	ln -s ~/.vim.vimrc ~/.vimrc

Plugin installation:
    Run next command in vim

    :PluginInstall
    
